c898dd5c227b4364c93705885f8c053f489","tid":1606533,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T20:48:39.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"9fde71e725108f82b77fc8d08f1437bc33ca7a8d","tid":1606533,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ead9f71795f41b1ed1fdb2b2a9bbf9e5d7217e4","tid":1606533,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"養 xx仲拖緊糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71c1f1569d011dfd9874bd569fccda2405cd370","tid":1606533,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ead9f71795f41b1ed1fdb2b2a9bbf9e5d7217e4","tid":1606533,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"養 xx仲拖緊糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多d"},{"pid":"de77c4a7f310dc92b5a9528958609c5052e39d82","tid":1606533,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e71c1f1569d011dfd9874bd569fccda2405cd370","tid":1606533,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ead9f71795f41b1ed1fdb2b2a9bbf9e5d7217e4","tid":1606533,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"養 xx仲拖緊糧<img src=\"/asset